snippet.title: Kaalia (HD) - Amitabh Bachchan | Parveen Babi | Pran - Superhit Hindi Movie (With Eng Subtitles)
snippet.description:
Kallu is forced to resort to robbing money from the safe of Shahani Seth, when he refuses to give him 500 Rs for his brother's treatment. Kallu is then sent to prison where he meets hardened criminals. After learning the tricks of the world of crime Kallu escapes from jail and vows to take revenge by destroying Shahani Seth's business. Watch how the innocent Kallu becomes Kaalia and brings about the downfall of Shahani Seth. WAtch the movie to know more.


YOR - 1981
Star Cast - Amitabh Bachchan, Pran, Parveen Babi, Amjad Khan, Asha Parekh
Director – Sohanlal Kanwar
Producer – Mahendra Gandhi, Iqbal Singh
Cinematographer –  Pravin Bhatt
Music Director – R. D. Burman
Lyricist – Majrooh Sultanpuri
Story – Tinnu Anand
Screenplay – Tinnu Anand, Santosh-Taher
Dialogues - Inder Raj Anand 
Editor – A. Habib
